sentences: Together they were nominated for the 2014 and 2016 ARIA Awards for Best Classical Album for their albums Dido's Lament and The New Goldberg Variations.
In 2011 Chindamo, Black and friends (Daniel Farrugia, Philip Rex, Sarah Curro, Caroline Henbest and Josephine Vains) released Hush collection.
